{
  "1731070": {
    "name": "失落迷城：群星的诅咒",
    "steam_appid": 1731070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/93c401a53d3ada05118b4db902287878.avif?t=1763649406\" width=616 height=226 /></span>你将扮演少女希尔妲，一位年轻的北风军团战士，为寻找在亚弗斯这座诅咒之城失踪的父亲而踏上旅途。 游戏主打动态多变的战斗系统、为你提供兼具挑战与探索乐趣的平衡体验，让你既能在这丰富的奇幻世界中探索，发现古老被遗忘的秘密与隐藏的宝物，亦可挑战刺激惊险的关卡并在充满沉浸感的故事体验中做出抉择。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入<strong>《失落迷城》官方交流群（638578191）</strong>，与大家一起讨论亚弗斯的冒险心得！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/552ca63e41a5f78189eda7f47473a3b5.webp?t=1763649406\" width=620 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前往以古希腊为灵感的美丽城市亚弗斯，并<strong>探索</strong>精心设计的<strong>无缝开放世界</strong>。  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>轻度类魂</strong>的战斗体验中，对抗超过60种敌人与22个首领。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>组合和任意切换</strong>武器，在战斗中尽情展现自我风格。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索丰富且宏大的剧情与世界观，并<strong>决定亚弗斯的命运</strong>。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>寻找</strong>超过100种收集物，完成诸多的支线任务，并在多周目模式下重铸属于你的命运。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全新的Boss Rush模式<strong>“繁星试炼”</strong>下测试你的战斗技能。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/1652f437f3370c471753edf1f0e65f6d.webp?t=1763649406\" width=620 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/0c5a58f1b325ee8f8c724074ec1aef58.poster.avif?t=1763649406\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/0c5a58f1b325ee8f8c724074ec1aef58.webm?t=1763649406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/0c5a58f1b325ee8f8c724074ec1aef58.mp4?t=1763649406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到亚弗斯城，这是一座充满魔法与奇迹的美丽城邦，以古希腊和罗马帝国的文化与建筑为灵感倾心打造。 在这座美丽和危险兼备的城市中，有被迷雾笼罩的市集街区、幽暗阴沉的下水道系统，神秘且有奇幻生物出没的城边森林，以及充满闪烁水晶的巨大地下矿脉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/dd6e0401feda2482be393295556b4d02.webp?t=1763649406\" width=620 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/21f2d8f44bba7eb35817faba073dfb2e.poster.avif?t=1763649406\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/21f2d8f44bba7eb35817faba073dfb2e.webm?t=1763649406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/21f2d8f44bba7eb35817faba073dfb2e.mp4?t=1763649406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从多项远程与近战武器中挑选并组合出自己的偏好！ 天赋系统更让你得以拓展多种多样战斗的可能性。 武器囊括了<strong>剑盾、双刃、短枪、战锤、法杖、护腕</strong>，你可以使用法杖在远距离狙击对手，而在敌人靠近时立即切换成战锤将来袭者击倒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/d4fc26463b5fab665289fdc01acc3e4d.webp?t=1763649406\" width=620 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/96bb11548f70b467cf2d103b78badc8a.poster.avif?t=1763649406\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/96bb11548f70b467cf2d103b78badc8a.webm?t=1763649406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/96bb11548f70b467cf2d103b78badc8a.mp4?t=1763649406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亚弗斯不但有惊人美景，这座城市也暗藏了众多可令你血脉偾张的敌人。 共计<strong>超过60种的怪物和22个独一无二的首领</strong>，每一个都将为你带来别具一格的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/00ab0297c8a8e39cc4cf59228f50a454.webp?t=1763649406\" width=620 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/2a3df15d121acbcef0ce35163ffcf908.poster.avif?t=1763649406\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/2a3df15d121acbcef0ce35163ffcf908.webm?t=1763649406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/2a3df15d121acbcef0ce35163ffcf908.mp4?t=1763649406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>你所做的每个抉择都影响深远！</strong></i>你在亚弗斯的冒险行动将一步步揭开这座城市诅咒背后的真相，你可从各种对话事件、探索文件、动画演出，以及希尔妲的手绘图文日志拼凑出亚弗斯的精彩故事与传说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/348e5337110161dbf62155c02bef09e9.webp?t=1763649406\" width=620 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731070/extras/e0d53ca08c85dbd51106c064390290e9.avif?t=1763649406\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《失落迷城：群星的诅咒》的世界充满了秘密和不为人知的故事。完成众多支线任务，寻找收藏品，从<strong>“星穹之核的赠礼”</strong>赢得奖励，在全新的Boss Rush模式<strong>“繁星试炼”</strong>下测试你的战斗技能，并在能够继承角色成长的<strong>新游戏+模式</strong>下打造你的传奇！</p>",
